            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[# Fastband Core 0.1.2

## Highlights

- Adds the bundled Fastband Core User Guide, available from the FBC utility rail.
- Documents first-run setup, new environment creation, existing-environment import, OrbStack, Linear, AIM, Git, tmux, troubleshooting, and best practices.
- Adds FBM Brain synchronization for the living guide with provenance and checksum evidence.

This is an internal Sparkle update for controlled Fastband Macs. Review the guide after restarting FBC and choose **User guide** from the left rail.
]]></description>
